name: Our Planet
description: Our Planet is a TV mini-series starring David Attenborough. Documentary series focusing on the breadth of the diversity of habitats around the world, from the remote Arctic wilderness and mysterious deep oceans to the vast...

review.name: Best Netflix documentary series I've ever seen.
review.reviewBody: From the majestic narration to the incredible shots of nature and landscapes to the huge amount of information about Our Planet that is given to us, this documentary series never failed to impress me and is the best Netflix documentary series I've ever seen.

trailer.name: Official Trailer
trailer.description: Filmed over four years, "Our Planet" is an eight-part series that promises an unprecedented look at the planet's remaining wilderness areas and their animal inhabitants.
